#ArtistFeature 🎨The tattoo scene in Prague is rapidly gaining prominence. Leading the charge is Michal Hanzlicek, (@hanzloch_tattoo) a former snowboarder turned microrealist tattoo artist. Born into a skateboarding family and surrounded by the inked and adventurous, Hanzlicek’s journey into the world of tattooing was one shaped by diverse influences. In our latest Artist Feature, we delve into Michal’s world, exploring his evolution as an artist, his unparalleled dedication to the craft, and his vision for the future.⁠
⁠
🔗 Click the link in our bio to read.
